<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_1335601'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1335601.The_Willows"><img alt="The Willows" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348548258l/1335601._SX98_.jpg" />
