<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer13515606344702135388">William Hope Hodgson was an English author. He produced a large body of work, consisting of essays, short fiction, and novels, spanning several overlapping genres including horror, fantastic fiction, and science fiction. Early in his writing career he dedicated effort to poetry, although few of his poems were published during his lifetime. He also attracted some notice as a photographer and achiev</span>
  <span id="freeText13515606344702135388" style="display:none">William Hope Hodgson was an English author. He produced a large body of work, consisting of essays, short fiction, and novels, spanning several overlapping genres including horror, fantastic fiction, and science fiction. Early in his writing career he dedicated effort to poetry, although few of his poems were published during his lifetime. He also attracted some notice as a photographer and achieved some renown as a bodybuilder. <br /><br />Hodgson served with the British Army durng World War One. He died, at age 40, at Ypres, killed by German artillery fire.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13515606344702135388" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

